descriptionHtml:
Adds Two spells Gods Blessing and Godly Shock both very overpowered. You can find Gods Blessing in Restoration and Godly Shock in Destruction. Open Console and type psb to make spells appear in magic menu. You can now also grab both spell tomes from the whiterun workbench from outside the warmaiden.

Sometimes it happens that the game crashes.
Write to the console:
help shock and help blessing
And find ID of spells.
Player.addspell <spellid>
author: Zyamum
